- @page_title = "You&rsquo;ve RSVP&rsquo;d for #{h(@event.name)}"

- content_for :other_content do
  %p Something about you having RSVP'd

.item
  %h2
    Woot!

  %p
    You&rsquo;ve RSVP&rsquo;d for
    %a{:href => event_path(@event)}=h @event.name

  %p
    If for some reason you can&rsquo;t make it
    %a{:href => event_rsvp_pike_path(@event)} tell us
    and you&rsquo;ll free up your ticket for someone else to attend.

.item
  %h2
    %a{:href => event_path(@event)}=h @event.name
    Details
  
  %p All the event details (time/date/place/link to map)
  %p A link to an ics file with the event details?

.item
  %h2 Present!
  %p Call to submit a presentation proposal.
  %p Info about what it takes to present.

.item
  %h2 Photos, Videos &amp; Blog Posts
  %p Reminder to take pictures/video at the event and tag them appropriately
  
.item
  %h2 Tweets
  %p Call to spread the fine word!
  %p Reminder for the tag
  
.item
  %h2 Tell a Friend
  %p Call to tell a friend. Harp on about "The more people the better, the more presenters the better, community driven event!"

.item
  %h2 Customise your profile
  %p
    %a{:href => edit_current_user_path} Customise yo.

.item.last
  %h2 Get the latest news
  %p A link to the blog and RSS feed